OL,3,CWomen dies after Kilkeel crash
OL,5,FA woman in her 20s has died following
OL,6,Fa two-vehicle collision in Co Down.
OL,8,FThe incident, which left two other
OL,9,Fpeople in hospital, occurred in
OL,10,FKilkeel on Monday evening.
OL,12,FA PSNI spokesperson said: "Shortly
OL,13,Fbefore 6.30pm, we received a report of
OL,14,Fa collision involving a white Audi A1
OL,15,Fand blue Mercedes Benz on the Newry
OL,16,FRoad.
OL,18,F"Officers alongside colleagues from
OL,19,Fother emergency services attended,
OL,20,Fhowever, sadly the woman was
OL,21,Fpronounced deceased at the scene.
