OL,3,CWomen dies after Kilkeel crash
OL,5,F"Two other people were taken to
OL,6,Fhospital for treatment for their
OL,7,Finjuries."
OL,9,FThe Newry Road was closed for a number
OL,10,Fof hours but has now re-opened.
OL,12,FPolice have made an appeal for
OL,13,Finformation.
